{"title":"美食系类","uid":"51740b82ceedddf663bb9047d4f24335","slug":"日常美食分享","date":"2023-08-11T02:13:36.000Z","updated":"2023-08-31T02:51:23.977Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/日常美食分享.json","keywords":"生活,美食,java,vue,Web开发,Linux","cover":"/img/photo-2.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"盐水鸡\"><a href=\"#盐水鸡\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"盐水鸡\"></a>盐水鸡</h1><p>1.食材的处理：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1、准备一个碗，放葱 姜  花椒颗粒，用温水泡二十分钟（根据鸡肉的量，来决定需要多少料水。）</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">2、处理新鲜刚宰的鸡，脱毛、洗干净</span><br><span class=\"line\">3、剁块，大小你们自己定</span><br><span class=\"line\">4、鸡腿和鸡翅部分要留整个的话，记得打花刀，打均匀，深一点。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">5、剁的鸡块放盆里，把第一步泡的料水，倒鸡块里，搅拌均匀，然后放 葱 姜末（碎一点，也别太碎），盐（可以多一点），鸡精，生抽，适量生抽（炸的话少放一点），蚝油，调味料（最好是麻辣味的），腌个一个小时左右，就可以了。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>2.做法：</p>\n<p>食材准备好了，你可以<font color='red'>炸着吃&#x2F;炒着吃</font>，炸着吃有两种，一种是带面的，一种是不带面的</p>\n<p>2.1带面的</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>想吃那种带面的，你就放鸡蛋，然后面粉将腌制好的鸡进行包裹，进行炸即可</p></blockquote>\n<p>2.2不带面</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>想吃干鸡块儿，你就炸的老一点儿，炸完一次炸个六七分熟，然后等油温上来之后再炸第二遍。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"炖猪蹄\"><a href=\"#炖猪蹄\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"炖猪蹄\"></a>炖猪蹄</h1><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">制作方法 </p>\n<p><p>1.准备食材。猪蹄两个、冰糖适量、姜适量、香叶两片、八角两个、干辣椒两个。<br>2.锅中加入适量清水，然后放入猪蹄，再加入少许料酒。大火烧开后，再煮三到五分钟，使猪蹄中的杂质充分煮出来。然后将猪蹄捞出备用。</p>\n<p>3.炒糖色。锅中倒入适量的食用油，然后将冰糖放入锅中，<strong>小火</strong>不停的翻炒。<br>4.炒至从锅底部开始往上冒黄色小泡即可。</p>\n<p>5.将猪蹄放入锅中，翻炒匀均。<br>6.将姜片、干辣椒、香叶、八角放入锅中翻炒匀均。<br>7.沿着锅边烹一勺料酒，然后再倒入少许老抽上色。</p>\n<p>8.加入适量的热水和盐。(水可以多加一点,因为要炖很长时间)大火烧开后，转小火炖一个半小时左右。<br>收汁。然后装盘即可。</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<br/>\n\n<p>::: danger  注意事项</p>\n<p>1、 猪蹄在做之前，一定要清理干净。如果有残余的猪毛之类的，一定要全拔掉。<br>2、 猪蹄不好剁开，所以在买的时候最好拜托卖家给提前切好块。<br>3、 炒糖色一定要用小火，炒至从锅底部开始冒小泡即可。火大或者炒的时间太长，口感都会变苦。<br>4、 炖猪蹄时间比较久，可以选择用高锅来炖。高压锅炖好后，再转到炒锅中收汁。<br>5、 收汁就是将多余的汤汁烧干。在收汁的时候要不停的翻炒，不然底部容易糊锅。</p>\n<p>:::</p>\n","text":"工作累了，以做美食当作一种放松！！！...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":903,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"美食","slug":"美食","count":1,"path":"api/categories/美食.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"美食系列","slug":"美食系列","count":1,"path":"api/tags/美食系列.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%9B%90%E6%B0%B4%E9%B8%A1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">盐水鸡</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%82%96%E7%8C%AA%E8%B9%84\"><span class=\"toc-text\">炖猪蹄</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"白兔","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/photo.png","link":"/","description":"一只刚刚入门的小白兔","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/whiteRabbit-me","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"Linux知识点","uid":"8a4f98118c8bb38b3f09443c20144804","slug":"Linux知识点","date":"2023-08-11T02:13:51.000Z","updated":"2023-08-11T09:22:53.345Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Linux知识点.json","keywords":"